OL,3,CUS demands Iran publicly guarantees
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz is open and safe for
OL,5,Cships
OL,7,FIran must publicly state the Strait of
OL,8,FHormuz is open and that ships using
OL,9,Fthe vital waterway will not be
OL,10,Fattacked, the US has demanded.
OL,12,FOfficials have blamed the latest
OL,13,Fstrikes against vessels, which sparked
OL,14,Frenewed hostilities this week, on a
OL,15,Fpower struggle in Tehran with rogue
OL,16,Fhardliners seeking to derail the
OL,17,Ffragile truce.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
