OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1783741698
OL,3,CUS demands Iran publicly guarantees
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz is open and safe for
OL,5,Cships
OL,7,FIt comes after Donald Trump said the
OL,8,FUS has agreed to continue talks with
OL,9,FIran following recent clashes but
OL,10,Fstressed in "no uncertain terms" that
OL,11,Fthe ceasefire was over.
OL,13,FBut just as Washington was seeking
OL,14,Fpublic guarantees over the strait,
OL,15,FTehran's top diplomat at the United
OL,16,FNations insisted any activity in the
OL,17,FGulf channel, "rests exclusively with
OL,18,FIran".
OL,26,@rD@MOUrD@`O]yD@OOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
