OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1783741698
OL,3,CUS demands Iran publicly guarantees
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz is open and safe for
OL,5,Cships
OL,7,FIran's ambassador to the UN, Amir
OL,8,FSaeid Iravani said on Friday: "Any
OL,9,Fattempt, by external actors, to
OL,10,Finterfere with or establish a power
OL,11,Farrangement would violate the (interim
OL,12,Fdeal), and undermine its
OL,13,Fimplementation, delay the restoration
OL,14,Fof normal commercial navigation,
OL,15,Fjeopardise maritime safety, and
OL,16,Fincrease regional tensions."
OL,26,@pD@_OUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
