OL,3,CUS demands Iran publicly guarantees
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz is open and safe for
OL,5,Cships
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the US military has been
OL,8,Fworking to counter claims by Iran that
OL,9,Fit controls the sea route and that
OL,10,Ftransit is only permitted through its
OL,11,Fapproved designated routes.
OL,13,FNevertheless, shipping using the
OL,14,Fchannel has plummeted following the
OL,15,Frecent fighting, with traffic already
OL,16,Fwell down compared to before the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
