OL,3,CUS demands Iran publicly guarantees
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz is open and safe for
OL,5,Cships
OL,7,FEarlier in the week, the US president
OL,8,Fbranded the Tehran leadership "scum"
OL,9,Fand said it was "a waste of time"
OL,10,Fdealing with the regime, amid
OL,11,Fexchanges of fire after Iran targeted
OL,12,Fthree tankers in the strait, which has
OL,13,Fremained a flashpoint.
OL,15,FIn a post on his Truth Social platform
OL,16,Fon Friday, Mr Trump said: "The Islamic
OL,17,FRepublic of Iran has asked us to
OL,18,Fcontinue 'talks'.
OL,26,@pD@_OUpD@dO]qD@QOUqD@aO]xD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
