OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1783741698
OL,3,CUS demands Iran publicly guarantees
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz is open and safe for
OL,5,Cships
OL,7,F"We have agreed to do so, but the
OL,8,FUnited States has stated to them, in
OL,9,Fno uncertain terms, that the Cease
OL,10,FFire is OVER!"
OL,12,FThe trading of strikes has again
OL,13,Fcaused severe disruption to maritime
OL,14,Ftraffic in the critical sea route as
OL,15,Fwell as casting doubt on securing a
OL,16,Fpermanent end to the conflict,
OL,17,Flaunched by the US and Israel on
OL,18,FFebruary 28.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@NO]
