OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1783741698
OL,3,CUS demands Iran publicly guarantees
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz is open and safe for
OL,5,Cships
OL,7,FMr Trump has also suggested the US
OL,8,Fcould reimpose its blockade of Iranian
OL,9,Fports, having already pulled Tehran's
OL,10,Flicence to sell oil.
OL,12,FIn a further retaliatory move, the US
OL,13,FTreasury acted to crack down on a key
OL,14,Ffinancier to the Tehran regime, Dubai-
OL,15,Fbased banker and businessman Ali
OL,16,FAnsari, previously sanctioned by
OL,17,FBritain for his role in financially
OL,18,Fsupporting the activities of Iran's
OL,19,FIslamic Revolutionary Guard Corps
OL,20,F(IRGC).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
