OL,3,CUS demands Iran publicly guarantees
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz is open and safe for
OL,5,Cships
OL,7,FThe country's defence minister Israel
OL,8,FKatz said: "If we will have to return,
OL,9,Fwe will return with even greater
OL,10,Fforce."
